scenario:
I've drafted an OpenSearch mapping based on our Solr schema. Can you review it? Here it is:

```json
{
  "mappings": {
    "properties": {
      "title": { "type": "text", "analyzer": "standard" },
      "description": { "type": "keyword" },
      "product_name": { "type": "text" },
      "category": { "type": "keyword" },
      "price": { "type": "float" }
    }
  }
}
```

Our Solr schema had: title with a custom analyzer chain (standard tokenizer + synonym filter + lowercase), description as text_general for full-text search, product_name with a copyField to a catch-all 'search_all' field, and category as a string field.
